description: "Register your futsal team for the London Futsal League. Join our competitive leagues in Brixton and North Finchley."
ogTitle: "London Futsal League | Team Registration"
ogDescription: "Register your futsal team for the London Futsal League. Join our competitive leagues in Brixton and North Finchley."
ogUrl: "team.html"
activePage: ""
hasAside: true
extraCss:
  - "/css/forms.css"
pageScripts:
